nodes.text: Return of the Jedi Weekly 83 is the eighty-third issue of Return of the Jedi Weekly, the continuation of the Marvel Star Wars UK series.
This issue reprints part three of a story printed in the US as Star Wars 91, along with part four of Star Wars 51.
Also included is a story titled R2-D2's tales from the Data Banks, which just reprints a non-Star Wars short story from Marvel Comics' Tales to Astonish #45, titled "Bronson's Brain."
